Have a look at `wrapperGetAjaxKey` from the [ZeroFrame API](http://127.0.0.1:43110/1DocsYf2tZVVMEMJFHiDsppmFicZCWkVv1/site_development/zeroframe_api_reference/) and try adding `ajax_key` like:

```js
zeroframe.cmd('wrapperGetAjaxKey', {}, key => {
  fetch(`http://127.0.0.1:43110/foo.bit/data/list.json?ajax_key=${key}&request=bar`);
});
```
